{"tid":1295051,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"泰迪寸爆美斯：要接受輸波","createTime":"2019-07-08T02:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T03:24:46.000Z","uid":31626,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b53d3f1a68cf32a2c10936cfdd8b6183fedf5433","tid":1295051,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:04:36.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】巴西贏得美洲國家盃，主帥泰迪不忘回應美斯較早前對賽事所作出的批評。<br />\n<br />\n「他必須展示一些尊重，當他輸波的時候，必須了解及接受。」泰迪率領巴西在周日美洲國家盃以3:1打敗秘魯，第9度贏得賽事錦標後，特別回應阿根廷球王美斯的言論：「他承受很大的壓力。所有人都有自己的問題，你必須懂得尊重。」<br />\n<br />\n賽前已否認會在決賽後離任的泰迪，領軍奪冠後被球員拋高，據報他極有可能在明年的美洲國家盃繼續領軍。<br />\n<br />\n美斯於阿根廷在4強戰受挫於巴西之役被驅逐離場，他指球隊在今屆美洲國家盃受到多番不公平對待，並怒轟賽會「腐敗」，為了將巴西推上冠軍寶座無所不用其極。"},{"pid":"03149a80ec680f03f3f23ff42eeb36f621457ec8","tid":1295051,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:07:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9c51fef0ee35bb0c23fc646c98e8e4a1eb25a2","tid":1295051,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13b7c9b23aa7746c232cda1576f5eec64bb497e","tid":1295051,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:36:40.000Z","msg":"收左足總錢？"},{"pid":"fbdc072e6760d7a5e8f2b9f90fb083dcca3646b4","tid":1295051,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2563c830a5174276842228a0e8f1d4ba580633d7","tid":1295051,"uid":37827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"我而家將佢命名為 串爆 美斯既fans 得未？"},{"pid":"45c0fc39d56a508b6127cd757244865a31685627","tid":1295051,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:27:32.000Z","msg":"明年的美洲國家盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a384